{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:d","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"double"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"zoomLevel"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In addition to affecting the visual size and detail of features on the map,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the zoom level affects the size of the vector tiles that are loaded. At zoom","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"level 0, each tile covers the entire world map; at zoom level 1, it covers ¼","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the world; at zoom level 2, ","type":"text"},{"text":"1","type":"text"},{"text":"⁄","type":"text"},{"text":"16","type":"text"},{"text":" of the world, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"so on.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to animate the change, use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setZoomLevel:animated:"},{"type":"text","text":" method instead."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/zoomLevel"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)zoomLevel","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1026","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"zoomLevel"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/zoomlevel"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"The zoom level of the receiver.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/zoomLevel":{"title":"zoomLevel","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/zoomlevel","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"zoomLevel"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/zoomLevel","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The zoom level of the receiver."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic"}}}